00:24:52.000 --> 00:24:56.000
 it's always very good to have the blessings of the lineage

00:24:56.000 --> 00:24:59.000
 as we're engaging with our practice

00:24:59.000 --> 00:25:04.000
 and so traditionally it is good to receive empowerment

00:25:04.000 --> 00:25:08.000
 and blessings to receive what's called the lung or the transmission

00:25:08.000 --> 00:25:11.000
 where someone who's been practicing

00:25:11.000 --> 00:25:15.000
 and especially has some realization of the teachings

00:25:15.000 --> 00:25:20.000
 reads them and we receive the blessings to take them into our own mind and heart

00:25:20.000 --> 00:25:25.000
 and then of course receiving the teachings is important

00:25:25.000 --> 00:25:29.000
 but most important is that we practice

